channel.title: Live: Wimbledon 2025
channel.desc: Live tennis from the All England Club, Wimbledon, with today's ladies' semi-final action deciding who will take part in Saturday's showpiece final. Presented by Clare Balding. Italian seventh seed Jasmine Paolini won the opening semi-final in 2024 despite losing the opening set to Croatia's Donna Vekic.
